    "message": message body,
    "type": "sms" / "call"
}

This is High Level CRM tool, you can do following methods:

1. Get Opportunity
{  "type": "get_opportunity" }

2. Get Contact
{  "type": "get_contact" }

3. Get Create Contact
{  "type": "create_contact", "data": { "email": "john@gmail.com",    "phone": "1234567890" }  }

4. Create Opportunity
{  "type": "create_opportunity",  "data": { "name": "new business", "contact_id": "EJa382nMuzgCek0AP9ec"  } }

